content: "Madonna gives free concert". NO. "Madonna gives a concert as a thank you to her fans". NO. MADONNA WAS PAID MILLIONS OF DOLLARS BY A BRAZILIAN BANK TO PLAY AT THE BEACH. Don't make this piece of news sound like she was doing something out of the kindness of her heart. She's a professional, got paid and did NOTHING as a mere "thank you" to fans.
